criteria_from_actual_contract_translated:
Tyres: Technical component. For tyres (winter and summer) with energy class C, equal to the energy class required in the specifications, it will be awarded 0 points, and the offers will be evaluated and scored as follows:
- tyres with energy class C = 0 points;
- tyres with energy class B = 5 points;
