Evaluation factor no. 4: Delivery time. The maximum delivery, installation and commissioning time accepted by the contracting authority for all the offered equipment and accessories is 4 months. Offers that do not fall within this period will be rejected as non-compliant.
For offers that propose a delivery time of 1 month from the date of signing the contract for all the offered equipment and their accessories, 15 points will be awarded;
For offers that propose a delivery time of 2 months from the date of signing the contract for all the offered equipment and their accessories, 10 points will be awarded;
For offers that propose a delivery time of 3 months from the date of signing the contract for all the offered equipment and their accessories, 5 points will be awarded;
If the delivery time proposed under evaluation factor 4 together with the installation and commissioning time offered under evaluation factor 5 exceeds the maximum delivery, installation and commissioning time of 4 months, the offer will be declared non-compliant.
